# Task 13 – Configure Virtual Agent

## Project

**Virtual Agent–Driven SLA Breach Awareness & Justification System**

---

## Objective

This task configures a Virtual Agent topic that provides guided assistance to IT support agents for SLA breach awareness, acknowledgement, and justification.

---

## Navigation

**Virtual Agent → Designer → Create**

---

## Topic Information

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Display Name | SLA Breach Awareness & Justification |
| Internal Name | sla_breach_awareness_justification |
| Type | Internal Topic |
| Role | itil |
| Visibility | Contextual |

---

## Conversation Flow

- Greeting Message
- SLA Guidance
- Decision Node
- Success Response
- Reminder Response

---

## Deliverables

- Virtual Agent Topic
- Conversation Flow
- Decision Logic
- Bot Responses
- Configuration Screenshots

---

## Expected Outcome

The Virtual Agent successfully guides users through the SLA breach acknowledgement process, ensuring mandatory fields are completed before the Incident is saved.

